SUMMARY:Easter: Kids Colouring Activity
DESCRIPTION:Calling all young artists! Grab your favourite Easter designs\, get creative\, and have a hoppin’ good time! 🎨 \nHow to Participate:\n🔹 Pick up a physical sheet at BCU Financial\, 2280 Bloor St W or download a digital version below. Note: If printing at home\, include the instruction sheet (page 7) on the back for your selected sheet.\n⬇ Download Colouring Sheets \n🔹 Submit your completed artwork at BCU by Friday\, March 27.\n🔹 We’ll display all entries in BCU’s windows from March 30 – April 15.\n🔹 Every entry gets a prize! Visit the same location between April 4 – 15 to collect the prize. \n\nGuidelines:\n🐰 Open to children 12 and under.\n🐰 Use any medium you like—pencils\, crayons\, markers\, etc.\n🐰 Submit your best colouring sheet.\n🐰 One prize per child. \n*Visit BCU Financial\, 2280 Bloor St W. during business hours. \nThank you to our Sponsors BCU Financial and Neighbur for supporting this activity.
URL:https://www.bloorwestvillagebia.com/event/easter-community-colouring-event-activity/
LOCATION:Bloor West Village\, Bloor Street West and Willard Avenue (South side of the Street)\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6S 1P4\, Canada
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/svg+xml:https://www.bloorwestvillagebia.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Colouring-Acitivity.svg
ORGANIZER;CN="Bloor West Village BIA":MAILTO:info@bloorwestvillagebia.com
END:VEVENT
