SUMMARY:Easter Hop & Hunt!
DESCRIPTION: 🐰 Bunnies are hopping back into Bloor West Village! ✨\nJoin us for a FREE Village-wide Easter Scavenger Hunt on Saturday\, April 4th\, from 10 AM – 2 PM. \n🎯 Visit 30+ local businesses and follow the clues to spot hidden bunnies\, eggs\, and chicks. Solve the riddles and enjoy surprises* along the way! 🐣✨ Meet the Easter Bunny & Easter Panda\n🎈 Balloon Twisting & Magicians \n\n📍 Pick up your Scavenger Hunt booklet at one of our starting locations: \n1️⃣ The Village Holdings (RBC Plaza) | 2323 Bloor St W – Meet the Easter Bunny 🐰\n2️⃣ Turner & Porter | 2357 Bloor St W – Meet Easter Panda\, sponsored by Smith Proulx Real Estate\, & join the dance party 🐼🎶\n3️⃣ La Petite École | 130 Kennedy Ave – Mini Egg Hunt* for littles. Find Gillian Ritchie\, Royal LePage sponsored booth and enjoy the Balloon Twister and Enter To Win A Fabulous Prize. 🎈 \nComplete the hunt\, enter to WIN LEGO\, breakfast for 4\, and other fun prizes! \nBring the whole family and hop into a day of springtime fun and surprises! 🌷 \n(*while supplies last)
URL:https://www.bloorwestvillagebia.com/event/2026-easter-scavenger-hunt/
LOCATION:Bloor West Village\, Bloor Street West and Willard Avenue (South side of the Street)\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6S 1P4\, Canada
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.bloorwestvillagebia.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/DSC03460-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Bloor West Village BIA":MAILTO:info@bloorwestvillagebia.com
END:VEVENT
